  Type: Library
 Title: QFreeDesktopMime
Author: Matteo Bertozzi <theo.bertozzi@gmail.com>

QFreeDesktopMime is a Qt4 class for determining the MIME type of files using FreeDesktop Specification.

		http://freedesktop.org/wiki/Specifications/shared-mime-info-spec

How to:
	To compile test-mime example run
		For windows and Linux: qmake && make
		Fox Mac OS X: qmake -spec macx-g++ && make

	To Run test-mime example run
		./test-mime <directory path>


	How to Get Mime Info
		QFreeDesktopMime mime;
		QString mimeType = mime.fromFile("/home/theo/myfile.cpp");
		std::cout << qPrintable(mimeType) << qPrintable(mime.description());

